WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.600 --> 00:00:04.200
Let's start by talking about the camera. Now the camera is not just for taking

00:00:04.200 --> 00:00:08.310
pictures of your kids. The camera can be a great way to get quick input

00:00:08.310 --> 00:00:10.590
into the mobile device. For example you

00:00:10.590 --> 00:00:13.440
can snap a new profile picture or capture

00:00:13.440 --> 00:00:17.680
a QR code to transfer a hyperlink, or capture a map or a business card.

